Cassette recording of <a href="/wiki/Patrick_O%27Brian" title="Patrick O'Brian">Patrick O'Brian</a>'s <i><a href="/wiki/Aubrey%E2%80%93Maturin_series#The_Mauritius_Command" title="Aubrey–Maturin series">The Mauritius Command</a></i> read by <a href="/wiki/Patrick_Tull" title="Patrick Tull">Patrick Tull</a></div>
